    "name": "File Description\n\nTRAIN_snRNA2_9M.h5ad\n\nTraining dataset that is splitted from 9 : 1 ratio of original dataset.\u00a0\n\nn_obs \u00d7 n_vars = 1327511 \u00d7 36601\n\nEVAL_snRNA_ac_enriched.h5ad\n\nEvaluation dataset that is AC (Amacrine cell) enriched.\u00a0\n\nn_obs \u00d7 n_vars = 7070 \u00d7 36601\n\nEVAL_snRNA_bc_enriched.h5ad\n\nEvaluation dataset that is BC (Bipolar Cell) enriched.\u00a0\n\nn_obs \u00d7 n_vars = 27293 \u00d7 36601\n\nEVAL_snRNA_rgc_enriched.h5ad\n\nEvaluation dataset that is RGC (Retinal ganglion cell) enriched.\u00a0\n\nn_obs \u00d7 n_vars = 7681 \u00d7 36601\n\nEVAL_snRNA_no_enriched.h5ad\n\nEvaluation dataset without any enrichment. The majority of cells are ROD.\u00a0\n\nn_obs \u00d7 n_vars = 11977 \u00d7 36601\n\nEVAL_snRNA_amd_sample1.h5ad\n\nEvaluation dataset that is a Age-related Macular Degeneration (AMD) sample.\u00a0\n\nn_obs \u00d7 n_vars = 9583 \u00d7 36601\n\nEVAL_snRNA_amd_sample2.h5ad\n\nEvaluation dataset that is a Age-related Macular Degeneration (AMD) sample.\u00a0\n\nn_obs \u00d7 n_vars = 11471 \u00d7 36601\n\nEVAL_snRNA_public_karthik.h5ad\n\nEvaluation dataset that is from Hahn et al.\n\nn_obs \u00d7 n_vars = 4803 \u00d7 36601\n\nEVAL_BC_class.h5ad\n\nEvaluation dataset that contains all BCs from all 7 evaluation datasets\n\nn_obs \u00d7 n_vars = 16167 \u00d7 36601\n\nEVAL_AC_class.h5ad\n\nEvaluation dataset that contains all ACs from all 7 evaluation datasets\n\nn_obs \u00d7 n_vars = 26382 \u00d7 36601\n\nEVAL_RGC_class.h5ad\n\nEvaluation dataset that contains all RGCs from all 7 evaluation datasets\n\nn_obs \u00d7 n_vars = 13938 \u00d7 36601\n\nEVAL_HC_class.h5ad\n\nEvaluation dataset that contains all HCs from all 7 evaluation datasets\n\nn_obs \u00d7 n_vars = 366 \u00d7 36601\n\nEVAL_Astrocyte_class.h5ad\n\nEvaluation dataset that contains all Astrocytes from all 7 evaluation datasets\n\nn_obs \u00d7 n_vars = 50 \u00d7 36601\n\nEVAL_Cone_class.h5ad\n\nEvaluation dataset that contains all Cones from all six evaluation datasets\n\nn_obs \u00d7 n_vars = 2695 \u00d7 36601\n\nEVAL_MG_class.h5ad\n\nEvaluation dataset that contains all MGs from all six evaluation datasets\n\nn_obs \u00d7 n_vars = 1429 \u00d7 36601\n\nEVAL_Microglia_class.h5ad\n\nEvaluation dataset that contains all Microglias from all six evaluation datasets\n\nn_obs \u00d7 n_vars = 79 \u00d7 36601\n\nEVAL_Rod_class.h5ad\n\nEvaluation dataset that contains all Rods from all six evaluation datasets\n\nn_obs \u00d7 n_vars = 18627 \u00d7 36601\n\nEVAL_RPE_class.h5ad\n\nEvaluation dataset that contains all RPEs from all six evaluation datasets\n\nn_obs \u00d7 n_vars = 48 \u00d7 36601\n\nFine-tuned Model\n\nfinetuned_AiO.zip\n\nAiO stands for All-in-One. This zip file contains:\n\n\n\nvocab.jsonGene vocabulary dictionary\n\nid2type.jsonCell ID-to-type mapping\n\nbest_model.ptFine-tuned model file\n\ndev_train_args.ymlModel configuraion file that can be inherited\n\nrun.logTraining logs for the model\n\nREADME.mdImportant instructions if using this fine-tuned model"
